{{!--
  Vehicle / ACPA damage result card (Core p.112 / Maximum Metal p.4-6, p.54-56). Rendered via
  renderChatCard from applyVehicleDamageCore / applyVehicleDamageMM and posted with
  ChatMessage.create (the MM dice attach via rolls:[]). `systemLabel` is the localized "Core /
  Maximum Metal / Powered-Armor Damage" heading. `body` and `lines` carry the resolution narrative:
  the Core path passes fully-localized text; the MM/ACPA SDP narrative passes English prose (the
  rolled numbers baked in) whose colour emphasis is shared .result-* classes (no inline CSS) —
  localizing that sprawling, branch-heavy prose is a deferred i18n pass (see the apply* functions).
  Triple-stash because body/lines carry markup.
--}}
<div class="cyberpunk save-result vehicle-damage-result">
  <h3>{{CPLocal "Vehicle.DamageResultTitle" actor=actorName system=systemLabel}}</h3>
  <div class="result-line">{{{body}}}</div>
  {{#if lines}}<div class="result-line">{{{lines}}}</div>{{/if}}
</div>
